plug in toaster
open bread loaf
remove slice of bread
  repeat step 3
  repeat step 3
place slice of bread in toaster slot
  repeat step 6
  repeat step 6
select toasting function
wait for function to end
else if toast does not possess desired doneness
  go back to step 9
else
  spread butter on toasted slice
    repeat step 14
    repeat step 14
else
  eat
